::----
::'''Mr. Xiyan:''' You see, you can't take care of much when you're busy. I almost forgot we agreed to meet.
::'''Mr. Xiyan:''' I've been keeping myself busy, coming up with the rest of the plot. But we may have a problem to which I haven't been able to find an answer yet...
::'''Mr. Xiyan:''' Based on your original story... After taking out the Disciples of Sanctus Medicus, you almost immediately fought your decisive battle against the Lord Ravager Phantylia. Don't you think that's pushing the story along too fast?
::'''Mr. Xiyan:''' If that's all I had, why, I'd finish telling this story in a single session. I wouldn't get the chance to set up one of my cliffhangers goading everyone into buying tickets for tomorrow. "Stay tuned for next time with Mr. Xiyan..."
::'''Mr. Xiyan:''' And I tell you what, the Protagonist Model isn't perfect enough if we do the plot this way. So, I've come up with an idea. I'm not sure what you think, so I'd like to run it by you...
::'''Mr. Xiyan:''' Nameless, you're not the only one, right? Those other heroes have also thrown themselves into this adventure. Is it possible to perhaps fudge things a little so that YOU will be the one doing those deeds?
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Wouldn't that make me a fraud!?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_812310108-->
:::'''Mr. Xiyan:''' Yeah, but... I mean, uh, no...?
:::'''Mr. Xiyan:''' What I mean is, could some of the Nameless' heroic deeds be pulled together and attributed to a single archetypal character?
:::'''Mr. Xiyan:''' Creating archetypes like this makes it easier for our audience to become emotionally involved. How about it?
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} That's okay, I guess. After all, I am the protagonist.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_812310112-->
:::'''Mr. Xiyan:''' I'm so happy to hear you say that.
::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_812310113-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_812310113-->
::'''Mr. Xiyan:''' So then, are there any companions whose exploits are suitable for us to add to our story?
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} There's one called Dan Heng...
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} There's this other companion who also came to Xianzhou...
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_812310116-->
