::'''Mr. Xiyan:''' Therefore, a drastic adaptation is required! We'll cut off everything apart from the beginning and the end. Maybe we can fix this story after all.
::'''Mr. Xiyan:''' I've got a rough idea... Let's go to Scalegorge Waterscape then. Perhaps we'll be able to find our inspiration beneath the Statue of the High Elder.
