:{{DIcon|Talk}} I've met your pet already.
::'''Mr. Xiyan:''' Ah, you met my little Youci~ How about it? Isn't it fascinating?
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Really, quite fascinating.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_817101503-->
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_817101503-->
:::'''Mr. Xiyan:''' Indeed! I knew you'd take a liking to it.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Not at all...
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_817101505-->
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_817101505-->
:::'''Mr. Xiyan:''' Not at all? *sigh* That's no surprise... The Nameless is vastly experienced. Nothing I have in my humble possession could hope to satisfy you~
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Actually, it was pretty weird.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_817101507-->
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_817101507-->
:::'''Mr. Xiyan:''' Hahaha, indeed! I actually think this "weirdness" is what's most fascinating about it.
::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_817101508-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_817101508-->
::'''Mr. Xiyan:''' So then, have you encountered any... special circumstances?
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} It chatted with me.
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_817101510-->
::'''Mr. Xiyan:''' Ah? It chatted with you? ...This... looks like she wasn't lying. This bird can actually... Don't mind me. I'm just talking to myself.
::'''Mr. Xiyan:''' Was there anything else? Such as... Did it give you anything?
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} It gave me a feather.
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_817101513-->
::'''Mr. Xiyan:''' Aha, I knew it'd gift a feather to you! They're really good, and you should take good care of it.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} What's the feather for?
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_817101515-->
::'''Mr. Xiyan:''' Just look at how light and transparent it is, like some small object sculpted from gemstone. Go sell it for money~ One feather is worth all you can earn across several days of storytelling!
::'''Mr. Xiyan:''' When you have the time, spare some time and chat with it more... I often find myself busy with work, and I fear it grows lonely. Seeing as it only chats with you, perhaps it has taken a liking to you?
::'''Mr. Xiyan:''' And besides, those feathers most assuredly are REALLY good~
::<!--Ends the current performance-->
