:{{DIcon}} The Hound Chases the Fox
::{{A|VO chapter2 2 xiyan 101.ogg}} '''Mr. Xiyan:''' Ah, new patrons I see! Looking for some refreshment at the teahouse?
::{{A|VO chapter2 2 xiyan 102.ogg}} '''Mr. Xiyan:''' Sadly there have been fewer and fewer bookings since the lockdown, so we decided just now to close the Sleepless Earl until further notice. We'll reopen once the Cloud Knights finish addressing their "security concerns."
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Did you see a foxian girl pass by here?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_102051905-->
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_102051905-->
:::{{A|VO chapter2 2 xiyan 103.ogg}} '''Mr. Xiyan:''' Unfortunately yes, the boss is never far away.
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Miss Tingyun... is your boss?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_102051907-->
:::{{A|VO chapter2 2 xiyan 104.ogg}} '''Mr. Xiyan:''' No, no, my apologies, different foxian. If it's Miss Tingyun you're looking for, she was here a moment ago...
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} (Show Tingyun's photo.)
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_102051909-->
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_102051909-->
:::{{A|VO chapter2 2 mar7th 120.ogg}} '''March 7th:''' Any chance you've seen this lady?
:::{{A|VO chapter2 2 xiyan 105.ogg}} '''Mr. Xiyan:''' Ah, so it's Miss Tingyun you're looking for...
::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_102051911-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_102051911-->
::{{A|VO chapter2 2 xiyan 106.ogg}} '''Mr. Xiyan:''' She ordered a cup of Immortal's Delight and went on her way. I saw her checking out the food stalls over there, that might be a good place to start.
::{{A|VO chapter2 2 mar7th 121.ogg}} '''March 7th:''' *sigh* Here we are sweating over our training while she's busy sampling dim sum!
::<!--Ends the current performance-->
